                    <h3 class=" p-work-overview--occ p-work-overview__title" id="project-overview">Project Overview
                    </h3>
                    <div class="p-work-overview__description">Sonum is a music streaming service that puts the social
                      aspect in the spotlight. Whereas Twitter, Facebook & Co are
                      about sharing more than ever - music streaming is heading in the opposite direction: a simple
                      exchange between person &
                      algorithm.
                    </div>
                    <img src="../../img/common/sonum-01.png" alt="p-work-overview-image" class="p-work-overview__image"
                      style="width: 80%" data-scroll data-scroll-speed="0.7" data-scroll-direction="horizontal">
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div id="the-challenge">
                  <div class="p-work-overview__container style=" transform: translate(0px, 0px)"">
                    <h3 class="p-work-overview--occ p-work-overview__title" id="the-challenge">The Challenge</h3>
                    <div class="p-work-overview__description"> The challenge of redesigning Sonum, a music streaming
                      service, was to create a platform that emphasizes the social
                      aspect of music sharing. While social media platforms like Twitter and Facebook focus on sharing
                      various types of
                      content, music streaming services often lack the social interaction between users and instead rely
                      heavily on
                      algorithms.
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div id="the-solution">
                  <div class="p-work-overview__container">
                    <h3 class="p-work-overview--occ p-work-overview__title" id="the-solution">The Solution</h3>
                    <div class="p-work-overview__description">Our solution involved stakeholder interviews to gather
                      insights, followed by information architecture, wireframing, and
                      visual design. We developed a design system for consistency and delivered a user-friendly,
                      visually appealing product
                      that met stakeholder goals.
                    </div>
                    <img src="../../img/common/sonum-02.png" alt="p-work-overview-image" class="img_sonum-02"
                      class="p-work-overview__image">
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div id="my-role">
