                    <div class="p-work-overview__description">
                      As a key member of the Sonum project team, my primary responsibility revolved around UX research
                      and design. Throughout
                      the project, I closely collaborated with the business analyst and development team at OneClick
                      Code (OCC) to establish
                      intuitive user flows for the team invitation and acceptance feature. I took charge of creating
                      wireframes and designing
                      the UI for the native and web app, as well as the mobile web app. Additionally, I played a vital
                      role in conducting
                      various research activities, which included:
                      <ul style="margin-top: 32px;">
                        <li>Stakeholder interview</li>
                        <li>Information architecture</li>
                        <li>Wireframes</li>
                        <li>Visual Design</li>
                        <li>Design system</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
